{"tid":1600743,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊入嚟抵制港獨餐廳加藤屋！","createTime":"2019-09-28T17:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T07:31:44.000Z","uid":135503,"like":408,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"35ef16cb5784b4930da15090e945ac3f8e6398a2","tid":1600743,"uid":135503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:24:32.000Z","msg":"話說有個支那媒體發現咗港獨餐廳加藤屋，仲吹雞叫人一齊抵制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZvT9qF7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZvT9qF7.jpg&h=edc2dc22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X4tYi08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX4tYi08.jpg&h=f7781840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌，我呢d咁愛蝈愛党梗係要關注下一齊抵制啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咦，不過佢quote香港加藤屋facebook，但抵制北京加藤屋wor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J8rV5Ku.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ8rV5Ku.jpg&h=f59de4ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嘩仆街丫，乜加藤屋食晒兩邊茶禮？<br />\n咁梗係直接問求證一下先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y0OA5L2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy0OA5L2.jpg&h=325b1633&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母，人地加藤屋剩係有香港業務，你班傻閪抵制間北京嘢做乜鳩呀，炒撚晒車呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span> <br />\n<br />\n縮係大陸想抵制香港，仲要錯鋪頭炒晒車，真係好撚驚呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d9648e2293de935b2a4aee6dd870aa4cc66c2d","tid":1600743,"uid":203332,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:25:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d95c05bde9949b571bb8a8a9586a7611ef48f28","tid":1600743,"uid":200550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:25:33.000Z","msg":"又抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4cfd4ef211847e39e1f238df9e2d9aa5d97f921","tid":1600743,"uid":135503,"like":96,"dislike":0,"score":96,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:27:06.000Z","msg":"加藤屋咁撚可惡，一定要懲罰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MyDmgYk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMyDmgYk.jpg&h=56f24667&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大大力用錢懲罰佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc1f791ddd46e363c8657e571f3cf0961fdbadf","tid":1600743,"uid":191271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:27:14.000Z","msg":"食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時支持率 82.2%<br />\n推到5000 人投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「光 復 香 港」  廢 除 《 聯 合 聲 明 》 第 三 次 公 投<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1600396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1600396</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"34a508c7c5122a57e0cfbcab6abf728767bd4dde","tid":1600743,"uid":298115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:29:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f88b74532b9f42d87bec6435078d62f2e9eab93","tid":1600743,"uid":322732,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:29:48.000Z","msg":"北京加藤屋表示: 躺著也中槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dffe5caac6cb42de8adb0b15a5c750adb9a6207","tid":1600743,"uid":135503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5f88b74532b9f42d87bec6435078d62f2e9eab93","tid":1600743,"uid":322732,"like":28,"dislike":0,"s